      "id": "stage-01",
      "order": 1,
      "title": "¿Qué es un porcentaje?",
      "html": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>¿Qué es un porcentaje?</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css\">\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js\"></script>\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js\"></script>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; padding: 1rem; }\n    h1, h2, h3 { margin: 0.2em 0; }\n    .badge { display:inline-block; font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 999px; background:#eef; margin-right: .4rem; }\n    .example, .task { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.8rem; margin: 0.8rem 0; }\n    .note { font-size: .9rem; color:#333; background:#fafafa; padding:.6rem .8rem; border-left: 3px solid #ddd; border-radius:6px; }\n    .tip { background: #f0fbff; border-left: 4px solid #6ac8ff; padding: 10px 12px; margin: 14px 0; }\n    .grid-visual { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(10, 1fr); gap: 2px; max-width: 200px; margin: 0.5rem 0; }\n    .grid-visual .cell { width: 18px; height: 18px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 2px; }\n    .grid-visual .cell.filled { background: #6ac8ff; }\n    .grid-visual .cell.empty { background: #f5f5f5; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<h1>¿Qué es un porcentaje?</h1>\n<div><span class=\"badge\">Eje</span> Porcentajes — Concepto</div>\n\n<p>Un <strong>porcentaje</strong> es una forma de expresar una cantidad como una fracción de $100$. El símbolo $\\%$ significa \"por ciento\" o \"de cada cien\".</p>\n\n$$25\\% = \\frac{25}{100} = 0.25$$\n\n<h2>Las tres formas de expresar un porcentaje</h2>\n<p>Todo porcentaje se puede escribir de tres maneras equivalentes:</p>\n\n<div class=\"example\">\n  <h4>Ejemplo: $25\\%$</h4>\n  <table style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:100%;\">\n    <tr style=\"background:#f0f0f0;\"><th style=\"padding:6px 10px; text-align:left;\">Forma</th><th style=\"padding:6px 10px; text-align:left;\">Expresión</th></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">Porcentaje</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$25\\%$</td></tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fafafa;\"><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">Fracción</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$\\frac{25}{100} = \\frac{1}{4}$</td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">Decimal</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$0.25$</td></tr>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Visualización con cuadrículas de $10 \\times 10$</h2>\n<p>Imagina una cuadrícula de $10 \\times 10 = 100$ casillas. Si coloreamos $25$ casillas, hemos coloreado el $25\\%$.</p>\n\n<div class=\"example\">\n  <h4>Representación visual de $25\\%$</h4>\n  <div class=\"grid-visual\">\n    <div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div>\n    <div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div>\n    <div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell filled\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div>\n    <div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div>\n    <div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div>\n    <div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div>\n    <div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div>\n    <div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div>\n    <div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div>\n    <div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div><div class=\"cell empty\"></div>\n  </div>\n  <p>$25$ de $100$ casillas coloreadas $= 25\\%$</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Porcentajes comunes</h2>\n\n<div class=\"example\">\n  <h4>Porcentajes que debes conocer</h4>\n  <table style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:100%;\">\n    <tr style=\"background:#f0f0f0;\"><th style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">Porcentaje</th><th style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">Fracción</th><th style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">Decimal</th><th style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">Significado</th></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$100\\%$</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$\\frac{100}{100} = 1$</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$1$</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">El total</td></tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fafafa;\"><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$50\\%$</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$\\frac{50}{100} = \\frac{1}{2}$</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$0.5$</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">La mitad</td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$25\\%$</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$\\frac{25}{100} = \\frac{1}{4}$</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$0.25$</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">Un cuarto</td></tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fafafa;\"><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$75\\%$</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$\\frac{75}{100} = \\frac{3}{4}$</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$0.75$</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">Tres cuartos</td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$10\\%$</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$\\frac{10}{100} = \\frac{1}{10}$</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$0.1$</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">Un décimo</td></tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fafafa;\"><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$20\\%$</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$\\frac{20}{100} = \\frac{1}{5}$</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">$0.2$</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">Un quinto</td></tr>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"tip\">\n  <strong>Relación clave:</strong> Para convertir un porcentaje a decimal, divide entre $100$ (mueve el punto dos posiciones a la izquierda). Para convertir un decimal a porcentaje, multiplica por $100$.\n  <p>$45\\% = 45 \\div 100 = 0.45$</p>\n  <p>$0.8 = 0.8 \\times 100 = 80\\%$</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"note\">\n  <strong>Recuerda:</strong> \"Por ciento\" significa literalmente \"de cada $100$\". Si $30$ de cada $100$ alumnos practican deporte, decimos que el $30\\%$ de los alumnos practican deporte.\n</div>\n\n<script>\ndocument.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function() {\n  renderMathInElement(document.body, {\n    delimiters: [{left: \"$$\", right: \"$$\", display: true},{left: \"$\", right: \"$\", display: false}]\n  });\n});\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>",
